org.apache.jena.riot

Class RiotReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.jena.riot.RiotReader

  • public class RiotReader
extends Object
    Operations to access RIOT parsers and send the output to a StreamRDF (triples or quads as appropriate). This class is probably not what you want to use. It is public to give maximum compatibility.
    See Also:
    for reading from a location, including web access and content negotation.
